Northern Trust Global Investments Limited: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 21, 2017 5:27 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Northern Trust Global Investments Limited



SnapshotÂ People




Company Overview
Northern Trust Global Investments Limited is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles, banking and thrift institutions, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, state or municipal government entities, and insurance companies. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm also manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. For its fixed income portion, the firm invests in money market and other fixed income securities of short and intermed...
Northern Trust Global Investments Limited is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles, banking and thrift institutions, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, state or municipal government entities, and insurance companies. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm also manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. For its fixed income portion, the firm invests in money market and other fixed income securities of short and intermediate term employing top-down macro-economic view along with a bottom-up analysis. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm uses external research to supplement its in-house research to make its investments. It is based in London, United Kingdom. Northern Trust Global Investments Limited operates as a subsidiary of Northern Trust Management Services Ltd.
Detailed Description


